description: Prague is full of the Slovaks. They have loads of opportunities here plus the local language is quite similar to their own. I like seeing them at my office because they´re always good fun. They all just love money. This cutie was no exception. He came to me seeking a career in engineering and I had a job open. The juicy salary made him interested immediately - he was completely broke. I´m sure you can see why I like them so much. Skint and greedy is the best combination. He was hard to bargain with but I could see he only wanted to increase his price. He was a little greedy bitch as usual. I have no idea how good were his engineering skills but he definitely had the other skills I was looking for. And his ass was surprisingly comfortable.
title: Dirty Scout 121
